public ImportRecords(String process)

Import Records class constructor

Parameters:
    process – Process to use when importing records. Supported values are:
ImportOrders: Import orders from Firestore for all active venues.
ImportPayments: Import payments from Firestore for all active venues.
ImportAll: Executes "ImportOrders", "ImportPayment" and "AssignOrdersToPayments" processes.

  Boolean updateRecords

Import Records class constructor

Parameters:
    process – Process to use when importing records. Supported values are:
ImportOrders: Import orders from Firestore for all active venues.
ImportPayments: Import payments from Firestore for all active venues.
ImportAll: Executes "ImportOrders", "ImportPayment" and "AssignOrdersToPayments" processes.
    updateRecords – if true, records are updated and fields CreatedDate and LastModifiedDate are not set.

Import Records class constructor

ImportAll: Executes "ImportOrders", "ImportPayment" and "AssignOrdersToPayments" processes.
    importDate – Only records originally created on this day will be processed.
    updateRecords – if true, records are updated and fields CreatedDate and LastModifiedDate are not set.

public ImportRecords(
  String process,
  Date importFrom,
  Date importTo,
  Set<String> venuesIds,
  Boolean updateRecords
)

Import Records class constructor

Parameters:
    process – Process to use when importing records. Supported values are:
ImportOrders: Import orders from Firestore for all active venues.
ImportPayments: Import payments from Firestore for all active venues.
ImportAll: Executes "ImportOrders", "ImportPayment" and "AssignOrdersToPayments" processes.
    importFrom – Only records originally created between importFrom and importTo will be processed.
    importTo – Only records originally created between importFrom and importTo will be processed.
    venuesIds – Contains a set of account Ids or venue Ids (ExternalId__c) and if included, only these accounts will be processed.
    updateRecords – if true, records are updated and fields CreatedDate and LastModifiedDate are not set.
